Package pw.ollie.politics.group

Class Group

  • java.lang.Object
    • pw.ollie.politics.group.Group
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<Group>, Storable
    public final class Group
extends Object
implements Comparable<Group>, Storable
    Represents a group of a certain GroupLevel in Politics which exists in a single Universe. A Group may have child or parent Groups and may or may not have direct members. It may also own land in the form of Plots.
